{"tid":2025207,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（召喚阿寶系列）港豬對大埔九巴事故已淡忘","createTime":"2020-05-20T05:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:31:12.000Z","uid":243422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b08b99aa42e90f69aa7fcc67550e74f984077855","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200520/mobile/bkn-20200520070017366-0520_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200520%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200520070017366-0520_00822_001.html&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krJAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=7782f7d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200520/mobile/bkn-20200520070017366-0520_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n巴士遲到車長畀人鬧？昨日（19日）網上流傳一段巴士車廂短片，一名車長在滿載乘客的巴士上，公然大聲指罵一名男乘客，雖然其行徑非常側目，不過網民獲悉事件來龍去脈後，不止未有狠批車長，反指車長發脾氣有理。<br />\n<br />\n片段由網民Ricky Chow於Facebook群組「柴灣人柴灣事」發出，事發前晚深夜，一架由深水埗往小西灣方向的118巴士車廂內，當時巴士停在路上。發文者指，一名男乘客疑不滿巴士遲到，上車後以粗口問候車長，結果惹怒車長反擊。片段開始，車長大聲質問乘客：「我依家問你乜X嘢事，X我老母」，乘客解釋「等得耐」，車長聽罷再「火起」：「等得耐關我X事」，又稱作為車長「全部睇時間開車」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的乘客似乎自知理虧，並沒有反駁，場面一度僵持。未幾，車長又再狂呻，稱自己不過「打份工，唔係帶個老母畀你X，你明唔明？」最後為免阻礙其他乘客，雙方約定到達藍灣半島總站後再行處理。整個過程司機非常火爆，車廂內其他乘客並無出聲，不過發文者稱，見到有人落車為車長「幫口」，自己落車時亦曾安撫車長：「我都唔該車長，遲到未必關你事的。」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民看過片段後都力撐車長：「趕時間搭的士！」有人表示：「巴士遲到唔一定關司機事，人哋打份工仲要受氣」；有留言稱涉事乘客行徑拖累全車：「係咪真係要出事先知咩叫禍從口出。」<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說：<br />\nTracy Lip：阻住成車人，搭的士啦~咁樣鬧人實在太冇品<br />\nVictor Leung：司機做得好<br />\nTony Yau：路面情況每日不同，車長控制到嘅做咗神仙啦，仲使坐喺司機位揸巴士？<br />\n<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100028056502603/posts/541141510164394/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100028056502603%2Fposts%2F541141510164394%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krJAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=d201084c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100028056502603/posts/541141510164394/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bef2949033c1d8673bbe2183e0adbc679f1ffae7","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"你依家一係躝落車等下架，一係我擺低部車等差佬告你公共巴士上講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb6704a00b3651b2e8ae34c0afa153449de429d","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"警世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40442415a3b555e8c289544b292e8780d859ef9c","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:29:28.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"659e6fdb3ead7e0530e98a0410bc4f7460a330e2","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"363a40683eabc8b47cb760970457f86808fa196c","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"70141f40d598177577999e61994988d7496c093a","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"9119468411600d0756febbc99ec767bc26d1c1cc","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:30:13.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"8d1f8c4fe80cbfa35394b3ef36ed7a1bb62dd5b8","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"0bea5809eddb33634d640f45be8eea6d7e1a42b1","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"自推7/10"},{"pid":"350eabe61b49c43419d87756d27db37f04e1ddc1","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"自推8/10"},{"pid":"23836ac98bab33bb221f1143c66f8cd54e6fdd95","tid":2025207,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:31: